		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Wondrous Item - Rare</em></p><p><em>This rusty iron sphere measures 3 inches in diameter and weighs 1 pound.</em></p><p>A creature can use this Iron Band to attempt to restrain a creature of Huge size or smaller.</p><p><strong>Action</strong> - 60 ft. - 1/Dawn</p><p><strong>Ranged Attack</strong></p><p><em>As the sphere moves through the air, it opens into a tangle of metal bands.</em></p><ul><li><p><strong>Attack: </strong>[[/attack]](Dexterity Attack)</p></li><li><p><strong>Hit: </strong>The target is &amp;Reference[Restrained] until you take a <strong>Bonus Action</strong> to issue a command that releases it. Doing so or missing with the attack causes the bands to contract and become a sphere once more.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Untangle Bands</strong></p><p><strong>Action</strong> - 1 Object (5 ft.)</p><p><strong>[[/skill athletics 20]]{Athletics Check}</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Success:</strong> The target is free and the Iron Bands are destroyed.</li><li><strong>Failure:</strong> Any further attempts made by that creature automatically fail until 24 hours have elapsed.</li></ul>",
